# 🚀 ML Projects Collection

A collection of beginner-friendly Machine Learning projects built using Python, Scikit-learn, Pandas, and Matplotlib.

This repository contains projects focused on prediction models, text classification, visualization, and basic Machine Learning workflows.

---

# 📌 Projects Included

## 📧 Spam Detection System
A Machine Learning based spam message classifier that detects whether a message is Spam 🚨 or Safe ✅ using NLP techniques and Logistic Regression.

### Features
- TF-IDF Vectorization
- Logistic Regression
- Spam Classification
- Confidence Prediction
- Visualization Dashboard

### Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

---

## 📈 SalesVision — Sales Prediction System
A simple sales prediction project using Linear Regression that predicts future sales trends based on previous monthly sales data.

### Features
- Linear Regression Model
- Future Sales Prediction
- Data Visualization
- Graph Analysis

### Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

---

# 🧠 Machine Learning Concepts Covered

- Regression
- Classification
- NLP (Natural Language Processing)
- Data Visualization
- Model Training
- Prediction Analysis

