---

# ⚙️ Installation

Install required libraries:

```bash
pip install pandas matplotlib scikit-learn
```

---

# ▶️ Run Projects

## Spam Detection

```bash
python spam_detection.py
```

## Sales Prediction

```bash
python salesvision.py
```

